# for Intellij PyCharm IDE
/.idea/

# Server Console build output — the Vite build of bitswan-server-console,
# embedded via go:embed at build time. The compiled bundles are never
# committed; CI (and local builds) generate them before `go build`/`go test`.
# Only the .gitkeep marker is tracked, so go:embed still compiles on a bare
# checkout.
/internal/daemon/serverconsole_dist/*
!/internal/daemon/serverconsole_dist/.gitkeep
